WEBVTT

00:08.084 --> 00:09.183
Why are you up?

00:09.185 --> 00:10.484
How am I supposed to sleep?

00:10.486 --> 00:12.386
I've been married
less than 24 hours,

00:12.388 --> 00:14.221
and my wife
isn't speaking to me.

00:15.525 --> 00:18.592
Perhaps you can think of this
in a more positive light.

00:18.594 --> 00:21.162
In one day,
you've managed to do

00:21.164 --> 00:23.764
what it takes many couples
decades to achieve.

00:23.766 --> 00:25.699
(knocking on door)

00:26.502 --> 00:28.202
Hi.

00:28.204 --> 00:29.336
Hey.

00:29.338 --> 00:30.237
You couldn't sleep either?

00:30.239 --> 00:32.506
Of course not.

00:32.508 --> 00:33.674
Me neither.

00:33.676 --> 00:37.178
But I just had
a tickle in my throat.

00:37.180 --> 00:39.613
Not profound marital problems.

00:39.615 --> 00:41.448
What are we gonna do?

00:41.450 --> 00:42.650
I don't know.

00:42.652 --> 00:44.885
Please, tell me
how I can fix it.

00:44.887 --> 00:47.888
Glad you asked.

00:47.890 --> 00:50.424
As I see it, there's
a simple solution.

00:50.426 --> 00:53.594
Your lips had a dalliance
with the lips of another woman.

00:53.596 --> 00:55.529
It seems only
logical that

00:55.531 --> 00:57.198
to restore balance
to the relationship,

00:57.200 --> 01:00.267
you should find another man
and dally with him.

01:00.269 --> 01:02.636
And by dally,
I mean some hardcore

01:02.638 --> 01:04.370
mouth-on-mouth action.

01:04.373 --> 01:07.274
Okay, that is the stupidest
thing I've ever heard.

01:07.276 --> 01:09.610
Actually, I think
he's onto something.

01:09.612 --> 01:11.378
Y-You can't be serious.

01:11.380 --> 01:14.315
'Cause I messed up
and made out with a girl,

01:14.317 --> 01:16.750
you're gonna do the same
with a random guy?

01:16.752 --> 01:19.420
I'm currently single.

01:20.957 --> 01:22.756
That's true. You are.

01:24.527 --> 01:26.994
What is happening?!

01:28.331 --> 01:29.964
I will tell you
what is happening.

01:29.966 --> 01:32.266
I am saving
my best friend's marriage.

01:40.009 --> 01:41.308
(gasps)

01:42.879 --> 01:46.513
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:46.515 --> 01:49.850
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:49.852 --> 01:51.485
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

01:51.487 --> 01:54.021
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:54.023 --> 01:56.690
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪<i> We built the pyramids</i> ♪

01:56.692 --> 01:59.360
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

01:59.362 --> 02:01.262
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

02:01.264 --> 02:03.230
♪<i> Bang!</i> ♪

02:03.231 --> 02:07.231
